Go to Apache maven and install the zip file 
Now extract it inside any folder

Now go to the environment variables and add the path of jdk to your system and environment variables.
Similarly add the path of bin directory of apache maven to the system and environment variables

now check if mvn is installed by doing mvn --version in a new terminal

add maven surefire plugin
add maven cucumber reporting plugin

in your pom.xml add these properties inside the properties tag
	<maven.compiler.source>13</maven.compiler.source>
	<maven.compiler.target>13</maven.compiler.target>

and navigate to your folder using cmd and run the command mvn clean install and a folder of name test-output will be created. 
	there in cucumber html report open overview-features.html
	